						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">King: Tribhuvanachchakravattigaḷ Rājarāja III Year: ⎯⎯</hi></p>						

						<p>Built in and incomplete. It seems to record a sale of two pieces of land, each measuring one thousand <hi rend="italic">kuḻi, by the sabhā</hi> of Paramēśvaramaṅgalam <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Chōḷakulatilatachchaturvēdimaṅgalam, probably for providing food on important auspicious days. </p>						

